[i]);\n+        if (status)\n+            return status;\n+    }\n+\n+    return FP_Q16_OK;\n+}\n \n I64 FPQ16Exp(I64 x)\n {\n*** End Patch\"'","aggregated_output":"","exit_code":null,"status":"in_progress"}}
